# web corpus explorer (issue #66): the frontend's node deps and the BUILT bundle are CI artifacts,
# never source. `npm run build` emits astrolyze/web/static/ (the wheel ships it as package data,
# built fresh in CI); a dev checkout that never built simply has no static/ and the explorer serves
# the API alone (web/api.py degrades gracefully). node_modules is install-on-demand.
astrolyze/web/frontend/node_modules/
astrolyze/web/static/

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
*.swp
